if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('IsFlagStop')
and type = 'U')
drop table IsFlagStop
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: IsFlagStop */
/*==============================================================*/
create table IsFlagStop (
id int identity(1,1),
MachineNo varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
datetimes datetime null,
stopdevice varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
DispathOrder varchar(50) null,
UnitValue int null,
constraint PK_IsFlagStop primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
go
